Title: The Big Dig: Traitor's Rest
Description: Don your cap, put on a pair of sturdy gloves, and grab a snack because Traitor's Rest is ready for Archivists everywhere to sink their history-craving teeth into!
ObjectivesText: Aid Eadweard Dalyngrigge and the Azerothian Archivists at The Big Dig in Traitor's Rest.
